WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.940 --> 01:39.270
[1998]

01:39.200 --> 01:39.920
Xiaolan,

01:40.590 --> 01:42.120
I know you're upset.

01:43.039 --> 01:44.840
But I lost my sister too.

01:45.640 --> 01:47.500
It hasn't been easy for me either.

01:48.509 --> 01:49.430
No matter what,

01:50.120 --> 01:51.720
you still need to study hard.

01:52.560 --> 01:53.690
As the teacher said,

01:54.200 --> 01:55.560
since it's your first time
handing in a blank test paper,

01:55.560 --> 01:56.759
they'll let it slide.

01:59.150 --> 02:00.350
Don't do it again.

02:01.200 --> 02:01.840
Okay?

02:26.960 --> 02:30.450
[Composition title:
The Answer to Happiness]

02:31.360 --> 02:34.570
[Episode 27]
[The Answer to Happiness]

02:36.000 --> 02:38.360
I'm more concerned about is—

02:39.310 --> 02:40.800
will we know each other at that point?

02:40.800 --> 02:41.930
Will we be together?

02:42.560 --> 02:44.240
Let me think.

02:45.000 --> 02:46.560
Let me do the math.

02:47.560 --> 02:48.630
Oh my god.

02:49.190 --> 02:50.150
At that point,

02:50.590 --> 02:52.590
you'll be an old man of 60,

02:53.150 --> 02:54.910
and I'll only be 36,

02:54.930 --> 02:56.090
in my prime.

02:56.120 --> 02:57.680
I won't fall for you.

03:01.470 --> 03:02.520
Alright.

03:02.800 --> 03:03.710
I'm kidding.

03:04.630 --> 03:06.030
I've confirmed it.

03:07.240 --> 03:09.440
The original me isn't in this timeline.

03:09.870 --> 03:11.070
And in that timeline,

03:11.470 --> 03:13.430
the current you doesn't exist either.

03:13.430 --> 03:14.800
So I cherish this,

03:15.310 --> 03:17.110
and I really don't want to leave.

03:18.680 --> 03:19.240
Alright.

03:19.630 --> 03:21.090
Let's not talk about this.

03:22.240 --> 03:23.120
Right now,

03:23.910 --> 03:25.440
you're right in front of me,

03:25.680 --> 03:26.740
and that's enough.

03:27.079 --> 03:27.910
What if...

03:30.310 --> 03:31.190
What if...

03:35.310 --> 03:36.280
I'll find a way.

03:37.150 --> 03:38.610
I'll definitely find you.

03:39.870 --> 03:40.630
But...

03:40.840 --> 03:41.710
you haven't seen

03:41.710 --> 03:42.710
me in that world.

03:43.520 --> 03:44.400
How would you know

03:44.400 --> 03:45.190
if that's me?

03:45.430 --> 03:46.490
As long as I see you,

03:47.079 --> 03:48.210
I'll recognize you.

03:48.840 --> 03:49.280
Just like

03:49.280 --> 03:50.280
when we first met.

03:51.800 --> 03:52.240
Fine.

03:52.680 --> 03:53.870
When you see me then,

03:54.150 --> 03:55.590
shout my name,

03:56.079 --> 03:57.480
and I'll know who you are.

03:58.560 --> 03:59.090
Xiaolan.

04:00.870 --> 04:01.400
Xiaolan.

04:02.840 --> 04:03.840
Xia Xiaolan.

04:05.710 --> 04:06.870
Xia Xiaolan!

04:08.590 --> 04:10.190
Xia Xiaolan!

04:17.310 --> 04:18.040
Okay, guys.

04:18.430 --> 04:19.390
She is the one,

04:19.720 --> 04:20.950
the only one, Ji Ya.

04:21.120 --> 04:24.270
My bride‑to‑be,
she's a famous fashion designer, guys.

04:24.480 --> 04:25.390
Please meet her.

04:25.390 --> 04:27.430
This is Patrick.

04:27.750 --> 04:28.360
Ji Ya.

04:29.750 --> 04:30.310
Wenxiu.

04:30.870 --> 04:31.730
My best friend.

04:32.240 --> 04:32.830
Hello.

04:33.000 --> 04:33.630
That is...

04:34.190 --> 04:35.430
my fiancé, George.

04:35.880 --> 04:37.440
My best friend, Wenxiu.

04:37.510 --> 04:38.400
G-George.

04:38.430 --> 04:39.360
Yes, that's me.

04:39.390 --> 04:40.430
That's so nice to meet you.

04:40.430 --> 04:40.870
Hello.

04:42.360 --> 04:42.750
Okay.

04:43.040 --> 04:43.990
I will...

04:44.159 --> 04:45.760
You can go. Okay. Sure. Sure.

04:45.770 --> 04:46.430
Take your time.

04:46.430 --> 04:47.630
Take your time, guys.

04:49.070 --> 04:49.600
Not bad.

04:52.630 --> 04:53.310
It's so big.

04:54.360 --> 04:55.159
Okay, thanks.

04:58.190 --> 04:59.630
I really envy you.

04:59.870 --> 05:01.000
You live so freely.

05:01.180 --> 05:02.120
You can go wherever you want

05:02.120 --> 05:03.520
and do whatever you want.

05:04.680 --> 05:05.190
And now you have

05:05.190 --> 05:07.450
such a handsome boyfriend spoiling you.

05:08.000 --> 05:08.600
Enough.

05:10.510 --> 05:12.170
People really are different.

05:12.390 --> 05:13.160
Growing up,

05:13.160 --> 05:14.690
you haven't suffered much.

05:15.680 --> 05:16.360
Well,

05:16.430 --> 05:19.000
I got divorced
and am about leaving my hometown.

05:19.000 --> 05:19.750
Is that what you call

05:19.750 --> 05:21.000
"haven't suffered much"?

05:21.000 --> 05:22.560
Let's not talk about unhappy things.

05:22.560 --> 05:24.480
Look how impressive you are today.

05:24.480 --> 05:25.430
Your brother and sister-in-law

05:25.430 --> 05:26.720
threw such a lively party for you.

05:26.720 --> 05:28.160
All your relatives and friends are here.

05:28.160 --> 05:29.000
Don't they hope

05:29.000 --> 05:30.560
that you'll have a better life?

05:30.560 --> 05:31.510
Of course.

05:31.720 --> 05:32.950
I can't let those

05:32.950 --> 05:35.350
who are waiting to laugh at me
get their way.

05:36.680 --> 05:39.010
I also sent an invitation to Tang Hong'en.

05:40.480 --> 05:42.480
Why did you invite him?

05:43.190 --> 05:44.390
Is that appropriate?

05:45.170 --> 05:46.600
Don't be so old-fashioned.

05:46.600 --> 05:48.270
What's inappropriate about it?

05:48.270 --> 05:49.000
It's just

05:49.000 --> 05:50.130
a farewell banquet.

05:50.310 --> 05:51.920
This is very normal abroad.

05:52.190 --> 05:54.159
Besides, George knows about it.

05:55.340 --> 05:56.870
I just want Tang Hong'en

05:56.870 --> 05:57.390
to know

05:57.630 --> 05:59.920
that I will live better without him.

06:02.270 --> 06:02.750
So,

06:03.430 --> 06:05.190
is he coming? Did he agree?

06:05.750 --> 06:07.360
I invited him graciously.

06:07.510 --> 06:08.430
As a mayor,

06:08.750 --> 06:10.560
would he be so petty?

06:11.630 --> 06:12.120
Cheers.

06:24.040 --> 06:25.840
Mom, you look really beautiful.

06:26.070 --> 06:28.360
It's the pearl earrings that look good.

06:29.240 --> 06:30.190
They are so big.

06:30.630 --> 06:32.040
They must have been expensive.

06:32.040 --> 06:32.700
Not really.

06:34.630 --> 06:35.430
Just to attend

06:35.430 --> 06:37.040
someone else's farewell banquet,

06:37.040 --> 06:38.270
we wasted so much energy

06:38.270 --> 06:39.530
and spent so much money

06:39.830 --> 06:41.070
just to prove a point.

06:41.560 --> 06:42.960
It feels like such a loss.

06:43.600 --> 06:44.070
Mom,

06:44.360 --> 06:45.430
the fact that you think this way

06:45.430 --> 06:46.360
shows that you

06:46.360 --> 06:47.870
no longer care about Ji Ya.

06:48.430 --> 06:49.390
Besides, she

06:49.390 --> 06:50.720
really isn't someone

06:50.800 --> 06:52.270
worth competing with.

06:52.950 --> 06:54.680
But what you just said isn't right.

06:54.680 --> 06:56.750
We're not spending this money on Ji Ya.

06:56.750 --> 06:58.430
We're spending it on ourselves.

06:58.430 --> 07:00.360
Women should dress up for themselves.

07:00.360 --> 07:01.240
That way, when you look at yourself,

07:01.240 --> 07:02.040
you'll feel refreshed.

07:02.040 --> 07:02.970
Don't you think?

07:04.190 --> 07:04.920
Besides,

07:05.190 --> 07:06.190
money is earned

07:06.190 --> 07:07.390
to be spent, isn't it?

07:07.510 --> 07:08.510
Even if Ji Ya looks

07:08.510 --> 07:09.510
rich and elegant,

07:09.600 --> 07:10.800
she's spending her family's

07:10.800 --> 07:12.430
and her American boyfriend's money.

07:12.430 --> 07:14.120
We spend the money we earn ourselves.

07:14.120 --> 07:15.160
We can spend it with confidence,

07:15.160 --> 07:15.630
right?

07:17.750 --> 07:19.870
I don't think this lipstick suits you.

07:19.870 --> 07:20.800
Let me change it for you.

07:20.800 --> 07:21.480
Not suit me?

07:24.750 --> 07:25.630
Try this one.

07:36.000 --> 07:36.920
Xiaolan

07:37.040 --> 07:38.430
is doing Fen's makeup.

07:38.620 --> 07:38.950
Yes.

07:38.950 --> 07:40.750
You'll have to wait a bit longer.

07:40.800 --> 07:41.240
Okay.

07:48.120 --> 07:49.270
You look

07:50.000 --> 07:51.360
quite anxious, huh?

07:52.190 --> 07:53.120
I'm not anxious.

07:53.720 --> 07:55.450
I'm just looking forward to it.

07:56.000 --> 07:57.930
If you're not anxious, have a seat.

07:58.360 --> 07:59.360
Okay, okay.

08:02.040 --> 08:02.970
Have some water.

08:03.000 --> 08:04.660
I'll have some water with you.

08:14.680 --> 08:15.680
Next, please welcome

08:15.680 --> 08:17.240
Comrade Liu Fen!

08:25.800 --> 08:26.480
What do you think?

08:26.480 --> 08:27.080
Is it okay?

08:27.190 --> 08:27.850
Beautiful.

08:28.510 --> 08:29.910
You are truly beautiful.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.950
Graceful and charming.

08:31.950 --> 08:32.830
Like a goddess.

08:33.270 --> 08:35.070
Adored by all, loved by flowers,

08:35.240 --> 08:36.970
so cute even cars would swerve.

08:39.030 --> 08:40.080
This bracelet...

08:42.030 --> 08:42.630
Granny Yu,

08:43.000 --> 08:44.330
this is yours, isn't it?

08:46.440 --> 08:47.040
Thank you.

08:47.910 --> 08:49.000
At the farewell banquet,

08:49.000 --> 08:50.150
how should I behave?

08:50.870 --> 08:52.200
Whatever you do is fine.

08:52.750 --> 08:54.790
If you see someone you like,

08:55.120 --> 08:56.480
just chat with them.

08:56.790 --> 08:58.480
If you don't like them
or feel uncomfortable,

08:58.480 --> 08:59.480
just ignore them.

08:59.840 --> 09:00.840
Just be yourself.

09:01.510 --> 09:02.030
Okay.

09:03.120 --> 09:03.700
Granny Yu.

09:03.700 --> 09:04.760
We're heading out.

09:04.840 --> 09:05.240
Okay.

09:06.440 --> 09:07.720
We're leaving, Xiaolan.

09:07.720 --> 09:08.250
Bye-bye.

09:08.630 --> 09:09.630
Wish you success.

09:13.550 --> 09:13.910
Okay.

09:14.360 --> 09:15.020
Let me do it.

09:15.520 --> 09:17.440
That bracelet is really nice.

09:18.240 --> 09:20.370
Do you have another one? I want one too.

10:01.240 --> 10:02.570
What are you looking at?

10:02.600 --> 10:03.670
Get to work now.

10:04.240 --> 10:04.960
Liu Fen?

10:06.510 --> 10:07.510
Hello, everyone.

10:07.950 --> 10:09.760
I am Ji Ya's brother.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.750
This is my wife, Caihong.

10:10.920 --> 10:16.570
[Ms. Ji Ya's Farewell Banquet]

10:12.960 --> 10:14.270
Today, my wife,

10:14.390 --> 10:15.150
Ya,

10:15.440 --> 10:16.670
and I would like to thank

10:16.670 --> 10:18.870
all our friends and family for coming.

10:19.280 --> 10:20.330
Since today

10:20.360 --> 10:21.840
is Ya's farewell banquet,

10:22.200 --> 10:24.060
let's invite Ya to say a few words.

10:24.200 --> 10:25.160
Who knows when

10:25.270 --> 10:26.670
she'll be back next time.

10:32.870 --> 10:34.070
Thank you, everyone.

10:35.270 --> 10:37.080
Since my brother asked me to speak,

10:37.080 --> 10:39.030
I'll keep it brief.

10:39.680 --> 10:40.280
You are all

10:40.290 --> 10:41.720
my closest elders

10:41.740 --> 10:43.430
and friends here in China.

10:44.000 --> 10:44.870
Although

10:44.870 --> 10:47.000
I've been back for a while,

10:47.630 --> 10:49.760
I've been so busy with trivial matters

10:49.960 --> 10:51.080
that I haven't been able

10:51.080 --> 10:52.360
to properly get together with everyone.

10:52.360 --> 10:54.150
And now, in the blink of an eye,

10:54.630 --> 10:56.150
I'm going back to America.

10:57.630 --> 10:59.830
I'd like to take this opportunity today

11:00.270 --> 11:02.000
to propose a toast to everyone.

11:02.120 --> 11:04.510
I wish you all smooth sailing

11:04.670 --> 11:05.720
and ever-improving days ahead.

11:05.720 --> 11:06.510
Thank you all.

11:06.510 --> 11:06.790
Come on.

11:06.790 --> 11:08.000
-Ever-improving days ahead.
-Ever-improving days ahead.

11:08.000 --> 11:08.480
Cheers.

11:09.200 --> 11:10.270
Thank you.

11:12.200 --> 11:12.790
Ya,

11:13.120 --> 11:14.510
this gentleman beside you,

11:14.510 --> 11:15.360
shouldn't you

11:15.360 --> 11:16.480
introduce him to us?

11:16.480 --> 11:17.120
Yeah.

11:17.150 --> 11:19.280
Do you have some good news to announce?

11:19.440 --> 11:19.910
Okay.

11:20.240 --> 11:20.910
I saw

11:20.910 --> 11:22.710
the diamond ring on your finger.

11:23.840 --> 11:25.480
Let me introduce him to everyone.

11:25.480 --> 11:27.790
This is George.

11:29.480 --> 11:30.630
He is my fiancé,

11:30.900 --> 11:31.540
because

11:31.720 --> 11:33.510
I just accepted his proposal.

11:34.790 --> 11:35.790
Hello, everyone.

11:37.320 --> 11:39.200
Thank you. Thank you, everyone.

11:44.290 --> 11:45.050
Hello, Sir.

11:45.080 --> 11:46.540
Do you have a reservation?

11:46.730 --> 11:47.470
We are here

11:47.500 --> 11:48.870
for Ms. Ji Ya's farewell banquet.

11:48.870 --> 11:49.630
Okay, it's in this hall.

11:49.630 --> 11:50.440
This way, please.

11:50.440 --> 11:50.790
Okay.

11:53.440 --> 11:54.630
If you change your mind

11:54.630 --> 11:55.750
and don't want to go in,

11:55.750 --> 11:57.010
we can leave right now.

11:57.600 --> 11:58.360
It's okay.

11:59.150 --> 12:00.350
I've decided to come.

12:00.480 --> 12:01.140
Let's go in.

12:11.390 --> 12:12.240
Why is he here?

12:14.320 --> 12:14.750
Ya,

12:14.910 --> 12:15.710
why is he here?

12:17.480 --> 12:19.790
It's interesting that he's here.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.530
That's her ex-husband.

12:22.320 --> 12:23.240
I thought people here

12:23.240 --> 12:24.370
were conservative.

12:24.480 --> 12:26.270
But... apparently not.

12:26.910 --> 12:29.910
Ji Ya and her ex seem to
have handled their relationship

12:29.910 --> 12:31.150
so quite well.

12:31.550 --> 12:32.750
Hold her back, quick.

12:33.080 --> 12:33.870
Mayor Tang.

12:34.200 --> 12:35.130
It is Mayor Tang.

12:35.150 --> 12:35.810
Mayor Tang.

12:52.120 --> 12:52.750
Tang,

12:53.000 --> 12:53.930
what do you mean?

12:55.480 --> 12:56.320
Nothing much.

12:57.550 --> 12:59.080
Ji Ya invited me repeatedly

12:59.150 --> 13:00.240
to attend

13:00.480 --> 13:02.720
her farewell banquet
before she returns to America.

13:02.720 --> 13:04.320
So I brought my family along.

13:05.270 --> 13:06.440
Since she's been so generous,

13:06.440 --> 13:07.370
I can't be petty.

13:09.320 --> 13:10.380
Is there a problem?

13:18.000 --> 13:18.730
Are you okay?

13:19.390 --> 13:21.360
How could I possibly feel well?

13:22.550 --> 13:24.630
Didn't you see he brought her

13:24.720 --> 13:26.480
to my farewell banquet?

13:27.030 --> 13:29.030
I'm leaving this country tomorrow.

13:29.120 --> 13:31.240
This is my last meeting,

13:31.440 --> 13:34.480
and he couldn't spare me
a shred of dignity.

13:36.270 --> 13:37.330
Do you want to stay?

13:40.200 --> 13:40.870
I'm okay.

13:47.550 --> 13:48.510
You just asked me

13:48.670 --> 13:50.480
if there was a problem, didn't you?

13:50.480 --> 13:51.200
No problem.

13:51.630 --> 13:53.240
I'm glad you came.

13:54.030 --> 13:55.200
I just didn't expect

13:55.870 --> 13:57.600
you to bring an extra person.

14:00.000 --> 14:01.530
Since you're already here,

14:02.150 --> 14:03.790
let's have a drink together.

14:09.960 --> 14:11.960
Liu Fen doesn't usually drink much.

14:12.510 --> 14:13.570
I'll drink for her.

14:13.720 --> 14:14.480
I can drink.

14:19.000 --> 14:19.840
No need to down it.

14:19.840 --> 14:20.970
Just a sip is enough.

14:26.150 --> 14:26.550
Ji Ya.

14:27.720 --> 14:28.600
We wish you

14:28.750 --> 14:30.150
a happy life in America.

14:30.750 --> 14:31.960
May you and George

14:32.470 --> 14:34.000
be together for a long time.

14:49.080 --> 14:49.880
Tang Hong'en,

14:50.000 --> 14:51.390
I was kind enough to invite you

14:51.390 --> 14:52.270
to my farewell banquet!

14:52.270 --> 14:53.330
And what did you do?

14:53.550 --> 14:54.030
You brought

14:54.030 --> 14:55.000
a shady woman here!

14:55.000 --> 14:55.550
Who knows which village

14:55.550 --> 14:56.600
she came from?

14:56.840 --> 14:57.480
I don't even know

14:57.480 --> 14:58.630
what kind of low-class,

14:58.630 --> 14:59.390
shameful methods she used

14:59.390 --> 14:59.790
to seduce you!

14:59.790 --> 15:00.630
Don't be so vicious!

15:00.630 --> 15:01.670
And you just brought her here like this!

15:01.670 --> 15:02.150
Enough!

15:04.550 --> 15:06.150
It doesn't matter what you say about me,

15:06.150 --> 15:06.910
but you can't,

15:06.910 --> 15:08.030
in public,

15:08.200 --> 15:09.120
fabricate facts

15:09.120 --> 15:10.960
and tarnish Comrade Liu Fen's reputation!

15:10.960 --> 15:12.020
Alright, alright.

15:12.790 --> 15:13.510
You claim to be

15:13.510 --> 15:14.910
from a scholarly family,

15:15.200 --> 15:16.930
so please watch your language.

15:17.240 --> 15:18.240
This event today

15:18.390 --> 15:19.320
is hosted by you.

15:19.600 --> 15:20.440
All these friends

15:20.440 --> 15:21.550
are here, because of you,

15:21.550 --> 15:22.910
to sincerely

15:22.960 --> 15:23.960
bid you farewell.

15:24.870 --> 15:26.600
So please have some self-respect.

15:26.600 --> 15:27.000
I...

15:27.020 --> 15:27.790
Tang.

15:28.600 --> 15:29.960
Don't think just because you're the mayor,

15:29.960 --> 15:31.490
you can talk to us like that!

15:31.600 --> 15:32.840
There are so many people watching.

15:32.840 --> 15:34.770
There are so many people watching.

15:35.080 --> 15:37.010
There are so many people watching.

15:37.030 --> 15:38.360
Let me speak for myself.

15:43.480 --> 15:44.030
Ji Ya,

15:44.480 --> 15:45.390
you're right.

15:46.200 --> 15:47.390
I am from a village.

15:48.390 --> 15:49.590
But that doesn't mean

15:49.960 --> 15:51.220
I'm worse than others,

15:51.750 --> 15:52.950
or lower than others.

15:54.120 --> 15:55.650
The countryside raised us.

15:56.050 --> 15:57.080
Although it didn't give us

15:57.080 --> 15:58.080
material wealth,

15:58.720 --> 16:00.320
the countryside taught us

16:01.320 --> 16:01.980
diligence,

16:02.270 --> 16:02.800
courage,

16:03.670 --> 16:04.470
and defiance.

16:05.870 --> 16:07.330
We refuse to yield to those

16:07.670 --> 16:08.870
who look down on us.

16:09.670 --> 16:11.150
We refuse to accept when people say

16:11.150 --> 16:12.010
we are unworthy

16:12.150 --> 16:12.950
or incapable.

16:14.910 --> 16:15.510
So,

16:16.000 --> 16:17.080
we strive

16:18.080 --> 16:19.880
to succeed just to prove a point.

16:20.450 --> 16:21.480
Every penny Xiaolan and I

16:21.480 --> 16:22.670
have earned

16:23.120 --> 16:24.750
came from our own hard work.

16:25.790 --> 16:26.750
It's clean

16:27.270 --> 16:28.320
and honest.

16:29.600 --> 16:31.000
In terms of backgrounds,

16:31.480 --> 16:32.320
since you were born into

16:32.320 --> 16:33.650
such a powerful family,

16:34.150 --> 16:35.550
I can't compare with you.

16:36.530 --> 16:37.140
But

16:37.160 --> 16:39.080
after all these years of hard work,

16:39.080 --> 16:39.910
I dare say

16:40.480 --> 16:41.540
that the current me

16:42.390 --> 16:43.520
is no worse than you.

16:51.670 --> 16:52.320
Well said.

16:56.120 --> 16:57.320
No matter who I am now,

16:58.000 --> 16:59.530
whether I'm a leader or not,

16:59.790 --> 17:00.920
please don't forget

17:01.720 --> 17:03.720
that I'm also from the countryside.

17:06.069 --> 17:06.790
Friends,

17:07.480 --> 17:08.740
I apologize for today.

17:10.480 --> 17:11.069
Let's go.

17:11.960 --> 17:12.829
I'll take you

17:13.160 --> 17:15.020
to your favorite tea restaurant.

17:16.109 --> 17:17.109
Whatever you say.

17:38.270 --> 17:38.800
Let's go.

17:39.610 --> 17:40.240
Calm down.

17:47.350 --> 17:48.270
I'm truly sorry

17:48.270 --> 17:49.270
about how things

17:49.590 --> 17:50.790
turned out today

17:51.400 --> 17:53.000
and made you so embarrassed.

17:53.790 --> 17:54.650
Actually, Ji Ya

17:54.790 --> 17:56.880
wanted fame and fortune through me,

17:57.270 --> 17:58.800
but I couldn't satisfy her.

17:58.960 --> 18:00.360
That's why we separated.

18:02.680 --> 18:03.590
But I think

18:03.880 --> 18:05.010
the end of a marriage

18:05.270 --> 18:06.470
isn't the end of life.

18:07.440 --> 18:09.350
If one is lucky enough

18:09.880 --> 18:11.340
to meet someone they like,

18:11.590 --> 18:12.650
someone suitable,

18:13.100 --> 18:15.360
that is the beginning of true happiness.

18:17.200 --> 18:17.830
Fen,

18:18.920 --> 18:19.640
I think

18:20.110 --> 18:21.160
I'm so fortunate

18:21.640 --> 18:22.510
to have met you.

18:23.310 --> 18:26.770
It all started when you fed me
that first spoonful of porridge.

18:28.480 --> 18:29.200
Today,

18:29.960 --> 18:31.360
asking you to the banquet

18:32.030 --> 18:33.690
was out of my selfish motives.

18:34.440 --> 18:36.040
Because the friends who came

18:36.650 --> 18:38.380
are people we knew from before.

18:38.880 --> 18:40.880
Since you're willing to come with me,

18:40.880 --> 18:41.590
our relationship

18:41.590 --> 18:42.590
is out in the open.

18:44.680 --> 18:45.310
I know

18:45.840 --> 18:46.550
you are actually someone

18:46.550 --> 18:48.250
who likes to keep a low profile.

18:48.250 --> 18:48.790
For my sake,

18:48.790 --> 18:50.450
you made such a big sacrifice,

18:50.960 --> 18:52.820
and I'm really grateful for that.

18:53.790 --> 18:54.960
And just now inside,

18:55.350 --> 18:56.410
the words you spoke

18:57.160 --> 18:59.270
really shocked me.

19:00.550 --> 19:01.350
You are so kind

19:02.070 --> 19:03.200
and so independent.

19:03.960 --> 19:05.290
You are so kind to others

19:05.790 --> 19:06.830
that for a moment,

19:07.070 --> 19:08.440
I wanted, in front of everyone,

19:08.440 --> 19:09.770
to ask if you'd marry me.

19:12.110 --> 19:12.790
But I felt

19:12.790 --> 19:13.880
that would

19:14.440 --> 19:15.400
embarrass you,

19:16.640 --> 19:17.480
so I dropped

19:17.480 --> 19:18.160
the idea.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.500
Let's take it slow.

19:22.000 --> 19:22.830
Everything

19:23.350 --> 19:24.510
will go at your pace.

19:25.400 --> 19:26.530
I'm willing to wait.

19:26.790 --> 19:28.390
I'm willing to wait forever.

19:29.400 --> 19:31.880
I also want to use this period of time

19:32.750 --> 19:33.880
to get my affairs

19:34.160 --> 19:35.090
in better order,

19:36.510 --> 19:37.030
so that you can

19:37.030 --> 19:38.560
let go of all your concerns,

19:38.710 --> 19:39.840
truly accept me,

19:40.470 --> 19:42.000
and truly, from your heart,

19:42.200 --> 19:43.200
want to be with me.

19:44.510 --> 19:45.920
I can't guarantee that in the future,

19:45.920 --> 19:46.920
I can give you

19:47.200 --> 19:48.270
a luxurious life,

19:49.030 --> 19:50.090
but I can guarantee

19:50.750 --> 19:52.150
that I will be good to you,

19:52.720 --> 19:54.450
and even better to your family.

19:55.640 --> 19:57.300
I will give every penny I earn,

19:57.790 --> 19:59.320
such as salary and bonuses,

19:59.590 --> 20:00.550
to you.

20:01.240 --> 20:01.880
And this money

20:01.880 --> 20:02.880
is all clean,

20:03.400 --> 20:04.400
so you can spend it

20:04.640 --> 20:06.040
with your head held high.

20:07.070 --> 20:08.600
I will help you earn respect

20:08.830 --> 20:09.760
and make you feel

20:10.000 --> 20:11.330
that being with this man

20:11.510 --> 20:12.200
is worth it.

20:16.350 --> 20:17.610
I can make my own money.

20:18.400 --> 20:19.930
I don't need to spend yours.

20:30.610 --> 20:31.610
I'm really sorry.

20:31.640 --> 20:32.350
I'm really sorry, really.

20:32.350 --> 20:33.000
We'll be going now.

20:33.000 --> 20:33.750
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

20:33.750 --> 20:35.160
Ji Lin, look at this mess.

20:35.520 --> 20:36.580
You should comfort

20:36.590 --> 20:37.560
Ji Ya first.

20:37.590 --> 20:37.880
Okay, okay.

20:37.880 --> 20:38.590
We're leaving now.

20:38.590 --> 20:39.680
Okay. Sorry you had to see that.

20:39.680 --> 20:40.510
Sorry for the drama.

20:40.510 --> 20:41.570
Goodbye. Goodbye.

20:59.880 --> 21:00.460
Ya,

21:00.620 --> 21:01.950
have you lost your mind?

21:01.960 --> 21:02.880
You invited him,

21:02.880 --> 21:04.350
and what are you angry about?

21:04.350 --> 21:05.160
Have you considered

21:05.160 --> 21:06.070
my feelings

21:06.140 --> 21:07.470
and George's feelings?

21:10.030 --> 21:11.310
I'm talking to you.

21:11.680 --> 21:13.340
You can disrespect yourself,

21:13.400 --> 21:14.240
and you can

21:14.240 --> 21:15.240
disrespect me,

21:15.640 --> 21:16.270
but what gives you the right

21:16.270 --> 21:17.680
to disrespect your brother?

21:17.680 --> 21:19.830
You just do whatever makes you happy,

21:20.030 --> 21:20.960
making your brother

21:20.960 --> 21:22.510
clean up your mess time and again.

21:22.510 --> 21:23.680
Look at yourself.

21:24.240 --> 21:25.310
Without the Ji family

21:25.310 --> 21:26.040
or George,

21:26.160 --> 21:27.510
what could you actually do?

21:27.510 --> 21:28.710
You fail at business,

21:28.740 --> 21:30.160
and you fail to keep your family together.

21:30.160 --> 21:32.290
You trample on everyone who loves you!

21:32.720 --> 21:33.780
Alright, alright.

21:34.590 --> 21:36.350
You're going back to America
tomorrow anyway.

21:36.350 --> 21:37.550
Do whatever you want.

21:37.710 --> 21:39.160
We can't control you anymore.

21:39.160 --> 21:40.490
Once you get to America,

21:40.790 --> 21:41.990
don't ever come back!

21:42.550 --> 21:43.230
Let's go.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.510
Ji Ya.

21:52.680 --> 21:53.270
Can you tell me

21:53.270 --> 21:54.400
what was that about?

22:10.070 --> 22:10.750
George.

22:12.510 --> 22:13.590
I'm sorry.

22:14.240 --> 22:16.000
I got you into this.

22:17.590 --> 22:18.880
I lost control.

22:20.290 --> 22:23.420
I don't know what came over me.

22:29.550 --> 22:30.200
Honey,

22:31.070 --> 22:32.240
can you forgive me?

22:35.880 --> 22:36.550
Okay.

22:38.510 --> 22:39.270
First of all,

22:40.590 --> 22:42.250
I hope you'll forget about him

22:42.640 --> 22:43.840
and forget about her.

22:44.880 --> 22:45.960
We go to America.

22:47.110 --> 22:48.270
It's just you and me.

22:50.200 --> 22:51.920
We start a new life in America.

22:54.070 --> 22:54.680
Okay.

22:56.070 --> 22:57.160
I love you.

23:00.440 --> 23:01.240
Are you sure?

23:03.110 --> 23:03.880
I'm sure.

23:08.010 --> 23:11.560
[Spring, 1992]

23:11.880 --> 23:12.750
Ms. Yu,

23:13.400 --> 23:15.060
since you're willing to meet,

23:15.110 --> 23:16.710
I won't beat around the bush.

23:17.240 --> 23:18.790
You are the General Manager of Elegance

23:18.790 --> 23:19.550
in name only.

23:19.920 --> 23:22.320
Actually, you don't get to make decisions.

23:24.510 --> 23:27.000
The real boss of Elegance now is Vivi,

23:27.920 --> 23:28.350
right?

23:29.160 --> 23:30.240
These are internal matters

23:30.240 --> 23:31.510
at Elegance.

23:32.150 --> 23:34.080
I don't need to explain them to you.

23:35.270 --> 23:36.200
True.

23:36.560 --> 23:37.440
Your internal affairs

23:37.440 --> 23:38.770
are none of my business.

23:51.090 --> 23:52.120
[Detailed Evidence Report on Elegance's
Alleged Infringement]

23:52.120 --> 23:53.150
[by Copying Luna Clothing Designs]

23:59.720 --> 24:00.750
What do you mean?

24:01.160 --> 24:02.030
Are you going to sue us?

24:02.030 --> 24:02.830
That's right.

24:03.440 --> 24:05.030
Since last quarter, Elegance

24:05.030 --> 24:06.890
has been copying Luna's designs.

24:07.680 --> 24:08.160
Ms. Yu,

24:08.160 --> 24:09.360
don't rush to deny it.

24:09.750 --> 24:10.750
We have sufficient evidence

24:10.750 --> 24:11.720
to prove it.

24:12.270 --> 24:12.830
Besides,

24:13.590 --> 24:14.550
you hired people

24:14.550 --> 24:16.640
to sabotage the construction
of Luna's store,

24:16.640 --> 24:17.440
cut the power,

24:17.880 --> 24:18.940
and smash windows.

24:19.440 --> 24:20.160
These things happened

24:20.160 --> 24:22.090
before you got to where you are now,

24:22.350 --> 24:23.550
so you might not know.

24:23.790 --> 24:25.520
But we have plenty of evidence.

24:29.480 --> 24:30.310
Ms. Yu.

24:31.350 --> 24:32.750
You're just an employee.

24:33.030 --> 24:34.920
I don't want to make things hard for you.

24:34.920 --> 24:35.680
However,

24:36.030 --> 24:37.680
please tell Vivi for me.

24:38.240 --> 24:39.500
After all these years,

24:39.720 --> 24:41.400
she hasn't improved at all.

24:42.270 --> 24:43.030
She's still using

24:43.030 --> 24:44.240
such dirty tricks.

24:45.030 --> 24:46.720
She really hasn't let me down.

24:48.070 --> 24:48.730
Three days.

24:49.270 --> 24:50.720
I'll give you 3 days

24:51.070 --> 24:53.270
to take down all the plagiarized works.

24:53.510 --> 24:54.240
Otherwise,

24:55.420 --> 24:57.620
I promise I'll sue you into bankruptcy.

25:02.680 --> 25:04.480
Do you have any other questions?

25:04.550 --> 25:05.950
I can answer them for you.

25:06.510 --> 25:08.110
I have no further questions.

25:08.350 --> 25:10.550
I generally understand the situation.

25:11.750 --> 25:12.350
Excuse me,

25:13.030 --> 25:14.090
I'll take my leave.

25:20.640 --> 25:21.310
Mr. Zhou,

25:21.480 --> 25:22.440
nice teamwork.

25:25.920 --> 25:26.450
Xiaolan.

25:27.680 --> 25:28.550
Xia Ziyu

25:28.550 --> 25:30.350
has stayed in Gangdao all along,

25:30.360 --> 25:31.440
but she seems to know

25:31.440 --> 25:32.570
every move you make.

25:33.750 --> 25:35.810
I am also very curious about Xia Ziyu.

25:36.270 --> 25:37.920
Next time I see Du Zhaohui,

25:38.270 --> 25:38.920
I definitely have to

25:38.920 --> 25:40.040
ask him all about

25:40.070 --> 25:41.730
his future young stepmother.

25:42.270 --> 25:43.360
Will Xia Ziyu

25:43.550 --> 25:45.080
really marry Du Chengrong?

25:45.590 --> 25:46.830
As long as there is a chance,

25:46.830 --> 25:48.560
she will definitely marry him.

25:48.880 --> 25:50.310
Only by becoming Mrs. Du

25:50.960 --> 25:52.200
will she feel secure.

25:53.970 --> 25:54.790
Alright, let's not talk about her.

25:54.790 --> 25:55.590
Let's go home.

25:56.160 --> 25:56.750
Ms. Xia.

25:57.550 --> 25:58.550
You forgot again.

25:59.070 --> 26:01.270
We are going to the flower market today.

26:03.070 --> 26:03.670
Oh, right.

26:03.960 --> 26:05.620
It's a good thing you're here.

26:05.830 --> 26:06.360
Let's go.

26:08.320 --> 26:09.510
I've been in Shengcheng for so many years,

26:09.510 --> 26:10.740
but I've never visited the flower market.

26:10.740 --> 26:12.200
I didn't expect it to be so lively.

26:12.200 --> 26:14.070
I should have brought my mom along.

26:14.070 --> 26:15.270
Do you see anything you like?

26:15.270 --> 26:15.800
This one.

26:17.590 --> 26:17.960
Here you go.

26:17.960 --> 26:18.620
You like it?

26:19.110 --> 26:19.550
Sir,

26:19.570 --> 26:21.070
this is a New Year mandarin orange tree,
right?

26:21.070 --> 26:22.000
Yes, it is.

26:22.200 --> 26:22.750
But

26:22.830 --> 26:23.750
you can't eat them.

26:23.750 --> 26:24.680
You can hang some

26:24.680 --> 26:25.920
small red envelopes on it

26:25.920 --> 26:27.110
with just a few cents

26:27.200 --> 26:28.270
or dimes inside,

26:28.480 --> 26:29.280
for good luck.

26:29.920 --> 26:31.450
This is quite interesting.

26:31.640 --> 26:33.030
Okay, we'll look around some more.

26:33.030 --> 26:33.790
Sure, sure.

26:34.200 --> 26:35.790
This Lucky Bamboo isn't bad either.

26:35.790 --> 26:37.070
We can buy 2 pots for the office.

26:37.070 --> 26:37.350
Yes.

26:37.960 --> 26:39.110
Pay for it!

26:43.310 --> 26:44.110
Do you like it?

26:56.310 --> 26:57.070
Ms. Xia.

26:57.550 --> 26:58.680
What a coincidence.

26:58.750 --> 27:00.480
Here for the New Year shopping?

27:00.480 --> 27:02.610
Let me wish you an early Happy New Year.

27:02.750 --> 27:04.480
Happy New Year. Happy New Year.

27:05.720 --> 27:07.520
Since we've run into each other,

27:07.640 --> 27:08.350
I have a few words

27:08.350 --> 27:09.550
to say to you, Ms. Xia.

27:10.240 --> 27:11.350
I know

27:11.550 --> 27:13.610
you are quite close to the Bai family.

27:13.750 --> 27:14.440
Please

27:14.790 --> 27:16.790
pass a message to Bai Zhenzhu for me.

27:17.350 --> 27:18.830
Because she is a woman,

27:19.030 --> 27:20.630
I have been going easy on her.

27:20.680 --> 27:21.240
However,

27:21.640 --> 27:23.070
tell her not to take things

27:23.070 --> 27:24.400
so seriously.

27:25.030 --> 27:25.750
Otherwise,

27:26.240 --> 27:27.720
I won't be polite anymore.

27:29.440 --> 27:31.440
Are you asking me to stop Bai Zhenzhu

27:31.680 --> 27:33.340
from stealing your business?

27:34.200 --> 27:34.920
Mr. Ke,

27:35.510 --> 27:37.880
in business,
it's every person for themselves.

27:37.880 --> 27:39.740
Why should I suddenly interfere?

27:39.900 --> 27:41.400
If you want both sides to sit down

27:41.400 --> 27:42.600
and negotiate peace,

27:42.770 --> 27:43.850
to divide

27:43.880 --> 27:45.210
business territories,

27:45.430 --> 27:46.410
you have to show

27:46.440 --> 27:48.040
an attitude of negotiation.

27:48.070 --> 27:48.830
Last time,

27:48.830 --> 27:50.750
you caused trouble
at Zhenzhu's birthday party.

27:50.750 --> 27:51.400
This time,

27:51.400 --> 27:53.350
you're making a baffling demand of me.

27:53.350 --> 27:54.110
Ke Yixiong,

27:54.510 --> 27:55.910
can't you be reasonable?

27:59.590 --> 27:59.960
Okay.

28:00.310 --> 28:00.720
Okay.

28:01.750 --> 28:02.270
Ms. Xia,

28:02.790 --> 28:04.640
then tell Bai Zhenzhu

28:04.920 --> 28:05.880
to wait and see.

28:07.750 --> 28:08.810
Enjoy your stroll.

28:08.830 --> 28:10.230
The goods here are great.

28:10.370 --> 28:11.150
Buy a lot.

28:11.310 --> 28:11.880
Goodbye!

28:12.200 --> 28:12.730
Goodbye.

28:14.880 --> 28:15.550
When did things get so tense

28:15.550 --> 28:17.350
between Zhenzhu and Ke Yixiong?

28:17.530 --> 28:19.350
After the brothers
at the Bai Martial Arts School

28:19.350 --> 28:20.650
have suffered for years,

28:20.650 --> 28:21.680
they finally found a way

28:21.680 --> 28:23.010
to improve their lives.

28:23.240 --> 28:24.510
And with Zhenzhu leading them,

28:24.510 --> 28:26.480
naturally, they're not afraid to fight.

28:26.480 --> 28:27.480
Ke Yixiong can't call

28:27.480 --> 28:29.140
every hooligan in Longcheng.

28:29.310 --> 28:30.550
And without guns,

28:30.960 --> 28:31.720
naturally, they can't win

28:31.720 --> 28:33.510
against the brothers
from the Bai Martial Arts School.

28:33.510 --> 28:35.110
He must have taken a beating.

28:36.790 --> 28:38.450
We still need to tell Zhenzhu,

28:38.550 --> 28:39.810
so she can be prepared.

28:40.600 --> 28:41.830
When we see her at New Year's,

28:41.830 --> 28:42.760
I'll remind her.

28:43.310 --> 28:43.840
Oh right.

28:44.510 --> 28:47.270
Since you're not returning
to Jingcheng this year,

28:47.270 --> 28:48.670
won't Mrs. Guan be angry?

28:49.790 --> 28:51.080
Ms. Guan Hui'e

28:51.110 --> 28:52.480
is very open-minded this time.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.880
She said she wanted to come to Shengcheng

28:53.880 --> 28:55.810
to see how Southerners celebrate.

28:55.830 --> 28:56.360
Alright.

29:07.750 --> 29:08.400
Granny Yu.

29:09.070 --> 29:09.920
My goodness.

29:09.920 --> 29:10.790
You haven't forgotten

29:10.790 --> 29:12.640
a single thing I taught you.

29:12.660 --> 29:13.160
How does it look?

29:13.160 --> 29:13.820
Beautiful.

29:15.200 --> 29:16.790
I remember you telling me

29:17.110 --> 29:17.920
that when you steam

29:17.920 --> 29:18.610
these buns,

29:18.640 --> 29:19.840
you make them blossom

29:19.880 --> 29:21.160
for good luck.

29:21.180 --> 29:21.860
Exactly.

29:22.160 --> 29:24.510
Birdcage shape and Grain mouth.

29:25.750 --> 29:26.920
I heard from Fen

29:27.200 --> 29:28.110
that in a while,

29:28.110 --> 29:29.770
you're moving to Shengcheng.

29:30.030 --> 29:31.960
After Tao finishes this semester,

29:32.030 --> 29:33.750
we'll move here next semester.

29:33.750 --> 29:35.000
Let him start high school

29:35.000 --> 29:35.860
in Shengcheng.

29:36.270 --> 29:37.720
It's a pity Xiaolan's house

29:37.720 --> 29:38.850
isn't finished yet.

29:38.880 --> 29:40.480
Otherwise, when you arrive,

29:40.510 --> 29:42.310
you could live in your own place.

29:42.550 --> 29:43.440
As long as the family

29:43.440 --> 29:44.950
can live together, it's fine.

29:44.950 --> 29:45.640
Whether the house

29:45.640 --> 29:46.720
belongs to someone else

29:46.720 --> 29:47.590
or us

29:47.590 --> 29:48.880
doesn't really matter.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.210
Look at you and Xiaolan,

29:50.550 --> 29:51.330
living with Granny Yu.

29:51.330 --> 29:53.130
Aren't you practically family?

29:53.160 --> 29:53.960
That's right.

29:54.030 --> 29:54.890
Let me tell you,

29:55.110 --> 29:56.310
when you move here,

29:56.350 --> 29:58.680
I'll teach you a few more tricks.

29:58.880 --> 29:59.940
That's wonderful.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.480
Granny Yu, Aunt, Mom,

30:02.550 --> 30:03.240
we're back.

30:03.270 --> 30:04.270
Tao, you're back.

30:04.350 --> 30:06.030
It's great to be near the sea.

30:06.160 --> 30:07.270
Everything is fresh.

30:07.270 --> 30:07.960
It's fresh.

30:08.000 --> 30:08.740
Go to the kitchen,

30:08.740 --> 30:10.030
and fill the big basin with water.

30:10.030 --> 30:11.090
Don't let them die.

30:11.090 --> 30:11.920
When we cook them tonight,

30:11.920 --> 30:13.000
they'll still be alive.

30:13.000 --> 30:14.110
Wash the chicken and everything

30:14.110 --> 30:14.830
and cut them up.

30:14.830 --> 30:15.790
We'll use them for soup later.

30:15.790 --> 30:16.230
Okay.

30:16.510 --> 30:17.110
Okay, Mom.

30:18.930 --> 30:19.920
Xiaolan and Zhou Cheng

30:19.920 --> 30:20.830
have gone to pick up his mother.

30:20.830 --> 30:22.230
They should be back soon.

30:25.550 --> 30:26.030
How is it?

30:26.030 --> 30:26.880
This is good. This is good.

30:26.880 --> 30:27.400
Looks good?

30:27.400 --> 30:28.350
It's fine. Just right.

30:28.350 --> 30:29.810
I'm pasting the left side.

30:30.390 --> 30:31.160
Watch it for me.

30:31.160 --> 30:32.490
Make sure it's aligned.

30:33.240 --> 30:33.590
Look.

30:33.680 --> 30:34.070
A bit more...

30:34.070 --> 30:34.480
Is that okay?

30:34.480 --> 30:35.270
A little lower.

30:35.270 --> 30:35.720
Lower.

30:35.830 --> 30:36.490
Okay. Okay.

30:36.680 --> 30:37.410
That's good.

30:39.170 --> 30:40.440
The New Year should be lively.

30:40.440 --> 30:41.750
Ask You Li to come too.

30:42.440 --> 30:44.370
She's at the hospital with her mom.

30:44.530 --> 30:45.240
I told her

30:45.270 --> 30:46.930
I'd bring her New Year's dinner later.

30:46.930 --> 30:47.560
She told me

30:47.590 --> 30:48.940
her mom is responding now.

30:48.940 --> 30:49.880
Sometimes when she speaks,

30:49.880 --> 30:50.740
she even cries.

30:50.830 --> 30:51.920
She said she never thought

30:51.920 --> 30:53.580
she'd be so happy to see tears.

30:54.750 --> 30:55.640
Wei.

30:55.830 --> 30:56.590
Now she tells you

30:56.590 --> 30:57.790
everything.

30:58.070 --> 30:59.640
You're almost there.

30:59.830 --> 31:00.640
No, no.

31:00.640 --> 31:01.070
Let me tell you.

31:01.070 --> 31:02.310
The revolution has not yet succeeded.

31:02.310 --> 31:03.710
I still need to work hard.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.580
Why didn't you ask San to come?

31:05.790 --> 31:07.550
San isn't from Shengcheng.

31:07.830 --> 31:09.480
He has to spend the New Year
with his family.

31:09.480 --> 31:11.210
Unlike you, hanging around here.

31:11.210 --> 31:12.570
How can you call it hanging around?

31:12.570 --> 31:14.890
Xiaolan's home is my home.

31:17.240 --> 31:17.790
Cheng.

31:18.830 --> 31:19.830
Hello, Mrs. Guan.

31:20.350 --> 31:21.480
Cheng, you're here.

31:21.640 --> 31:22.400
Xiaolan.

31:22.920 --> 31:23.310
Mrs. Guan. Hello, Mrs. Guan.

31:23.310 --> 31:24.030
You're here.

31:24.030 --> 31:24.750
Happy New Year.

31:24.750 --> 31:25.960
I heard everything,

31:26.000 --> 31:26.680
Wei.

31:27.210 --> 31:28.350
Aren't you afraid I'll tell your mom

31:28.350 --> 31:29.350
and second uncle?

31:30.110 --> 31:30.640
Hello, Mrs. Guan.

31:30.640 --> 31:31.270
Hello, hello.

31:31.270 --> 31:31.790
Mrs. Guan,

31:31.790 --> 31:33.270
you won't sell me out.

31:33.270 --> 31:34.480
Besides, I didn't go back this time,

31:34.480 --> 31:35.600
and they didn't come to catch me.

31:35.600 --> 31:37.000
You must have explained it to her.

31:37.000 --> 31:38.110
They didn't come,

31:38.110 --> 31:39.750
but they sent me to inspect.

31:40.160 --> 31:41.200
You'd better behave.

31:41.200 --> 31:41.930
Absolutely.

31:42.080 --> 31:42.720
Well, Cheng,

31:42.720 --> 31:43.510
I'll get them!

31:43.510 --> 31:44.070
Don't, don't!

31:44.070 --> 31:44.960
I'll get them! Let me do that!

31:44.960 --> 31:45.640
Here, here.

31:45.640 --> 31:47.070
I'll get them! Let me do that!

31:47.070 --> 31:47.750
You're here.

31:47.750 --> 31:49.110
Fen, Fen, Fen.

31:49.880 --> 31:51.010
Was the trip smooth?

31:51.160 --> 31:51.890
Very smooth.

31:52.310 --> 31:53.030
You know, Shengcheng

31:53.030 --> 31:54.160
isn't cold at all.

31:54.160 --> 31:55.310
It's so comfortable.

31:55.310 --> 31:56.270
-Really.
-Quick,

31:56.270 --> 31:56.920
come in.

32:02.310 --> 32:03.000
Wei.

32:03.250 --> 32:04.320
Don't eat too much.

32:04.350 --> 32:04.920
There's so much food.

32:04.920 --> 32:05.750
Today,

32:05.750 --> 32:07.480
we have a mix of North and South.

32:07.510 --> 32:09.040
We have customs from both.

32:09.070 --> 32:09.830
At 12 o'clock at night,

32:09.830 --> 32:10.750
we still have to boil dumplings.

32:10.750 --> 32:11.200
Later,

32:11.200 --> 32:12.800
I have to bring food to You Li.

32:12.880 --> 32:13.830
With this round trip,

32:13.830 --> 32:14.760
I can eat 2 plates

32:14.790 --> 32:15.590
of the dumplings at 12.

32:15.590 --> 32:16.190
It's fine.

32:16.790 --> 32:17.400
Fen.

32:18.200 --> 32:19.310
At this scene right now,

32:19.310 --> 32:20.840
guess what I'm thinking of?

32:21.240 --> 32:22.110
What?

32:22.640 --> 32:23.240
Are you thinking of

32:23.240 --> 32:24.960
the whole village crowding together

32:24.960 --> 32:27.030
on the threshing floor
to watch the Chinese New Year Gala?

32:27.030 --> 32:27.630
Is that it?

32:28.510 --> 32:30.200
My wife knows me best.

32:30.840 --> 32:31.770
I'm not like you.

32:31.790 --> 32:33.480
I don't like dwelling on the past.

32:33.480 --> 32:34.550
Look, our lives

32:34.550 --> 32:36.000
are getting better and better.

32:36.000 --> 32:37.240
Now, every day when I wake up,

32:37.240 --> 32:39.300
I only think about better days ahead.

32:39.440 --> 32:39.840
Right.

32:40.000 --> 32:41.080
Well said, Auntie.

32:41.110 --> 32:41.920
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

32:41.920 --> 32:43.550
-Cheers.
-Thank you, Xiaolan.

32:43.550 --> 32:44.880
To our better future!

32:45.070 --> 32:46.440
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

32:53.480 --> 32:54.310
These buildings

32:54.310 --> 32:55.880
are getting taller and taller now.

32:55.880 --> 32:56.680
In the future,

32:57.000 --> 32:57.660
this kind of view

32:57.660 --> 32:59.310
might be hard to come by.

32:59.830 --> 33:00.350
Mom,

33:00.750 --> 33:01.310
nowadays, buildings

33:01.310 --> 33:02.550
can also have good views.

33:02.550 --> 33:04.160
It depends on whether the builder

33:04.160 --> 33:05.240
puts her heart into it.

33:05.240 --> 33:06.310
Look at you.

33:06.340 --> 33:10.110
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

33:06.440 --> 33:07.680
Mrs. Guan, don't worry.

33:07.680 --> 33:09.880
The building I build
will definitely have great views.

33:09.880 --> 33:10.590
Definitely.

33:10.590 --> 33:11.000
Right.

33:11.240 --> 33:13.560
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

33:12.030 --> 33:12.440
Yes.

33:13.270 --> 33:13.750
Mom.

33:14.340 --> 33:16.630
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

33:14.550 --> 33:15.640
Didn't Mr. Tang tell you

33:15.640 --> 33:17.040
if he can come back or not?

33:17.790 --> 33:19.590
He's busiest during the holidays.

33:19.340 --> 33:23.540
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

33:19.830 --> 33:21.960
He has to visit the community
to bring warmth.

33:21.960 --> 33:22.560
It's okay.

33:22.750 --> 33:23.830
Let me,

33:23.960 --> 33:26.030
your sweet daughter, bring you warmth!

33:24.440 --> 33:26.950
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

33:26.400 --> 33:27.830
Xiaolan is the best.

33:26.970 --> 33:30.720
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

33:27.830 --> 33:29.510
It's better to have a daughter.

33:29.510 --> 33:30.830
I'm almost done eating.

33:30.830 --> 33:32.110
I'll go bring her the food while it's hot.

33:31.280 --> 33:33.680
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

33:32.550 --> 33:33.310
As for You's portion,

33:33.310 --> 33:34.680
I packed it separately.

33:34.720 --> 33:35.350
It's in the wok.

33:34.890 --> 33:37.460
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

33:36.160 --> 33:37.490
I'll get it. I'll get it.

33:38.200 --> 33:39.310
After Mom

33:38.300 --> 33:40.710
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

33:39.310 --> 33:40.830
marries Mr. Tang,

33:41.350 --> 33:42.240
she'll have to move

33:41.430 --> 33:46.310
♪ Our youth ♪

33:42.270 --> 33:43.400
to his place, right?

33:44.110 --> 33:45.440
Then poor me.

33:46.330 --> 33:49.860
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

33:46.920 --> 33:47.550
Then...

33:48.200 --> 33:49.460
let's get married too?

33:49.880 --> 33:53.260
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

33:50.680 --> 33:51.160
Great.

33:53.240 --> 33:53.790
Okay.

33:53.440 --> 33:56.280
♪ We never give up ♪

33:54.200 --> 33:55.200
But promise me,

33:55.480 --> 33:56.640
after we get married,

33:56.640 --> 33:58.350
I still want to live here with Granny Yu.

33:56.900 --> 34:00.120
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

33:58.680 --> 34:00.140
Otherwise, she'll miss me,

34:00.140 --> 34:03.370
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

34:00.270 --> 34:01.030
right?

34:01.440 --> 34:02.440
Exactly.

34:03.270 --> 34:04.750
This is your home.

34:03.400 --> 34:06.790
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

34:05.400 --> 34:06.200
Xiaolan, Zhou,

34:06.200 --> 34:07.510
we're waiting for

34:06.820 --> 34:09.870
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

34:07.510 --> 34:08.510
your big day.

34:09.550 --> 34:10.960
You have to keep your word.

34:10.340 --> 34:13.280
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

34:11.110 --> 34:12.710
The elders are all here today.

34:12.710 --> 34:13.920
You can't lie to us.

34:13.650 --> 34:19.630
♪ That'd be enough ♪

34:14.030 --> 34:14.440
Okay.

34:14.960 --> 34:15.620
It's a deal.

34:15.630 --> 34:16.090
Come on.

34:16.320 --> 34:16.980
It's a deal.

34:18.710 --> 34:19.840
Careful.

34:20.150 --> 34:20.670
Got it.

34:20.710 --> 34:21.510
Don't spill it.

34:21.510 --> 34:22.440
I'm heading out.

34:22.719 --> 34:23.630
-Careful.
-Be careful.

34:23.630 --> 34:24.150
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

34:24.150 --> 34:25.480
Barbecue pork buns are here.

34:25.480 --> 34:26.480
Happy New Year!

34:27.190 --> 34:28.110
Mr. Tang.

34:28.110 --> 34:29.030
Happy New Year!

34:29.320 --> 34:30.670
The Mayor is here.

34:30.670 --> 34:31.530
Happy New Year!

34:32.030 --> 34:33.070
Happy New Year! Happy New Year!

34:33.070 --> 34:34.000
Come on, come on.

34:34.020 --> 34:34.670
Hello, Auntie.

34:34.670 --> 34:35.630
Sit with Fen, come on.

34:35.630 --> 34:36.550
Where did you go?

34:36.550 --> 34:37.590
But now,

34:37.590 --> 34:38.630
you're about to become

34:38.630 --> 34:39.760
my brother-in-law.

34:40.510 --> 34:41.449
Comrade Tang.

34:41.920 --> 34:43.050
Here, take my glass.

34:43.080 --> 34:43.880
Drink a cup as a penalty.

34:43.880 --> 34:45.510
You must drink for being late.

34:45.510 --> 34:46.770
This is a good penalty.

34:47.150 --> 34:47.880
I accept it.

34:48.550 --> 34:49.210
Bottoms up.

34:49.280 --> 34:49.920
Happy New Year.

34:49.920 --> 34:50.250
Good.

34:51.080 --> 34:52.630
That's not just accepting a penalty.

34:52.630 --> 34:55.429
He's clearly acknowledging
his brother-in-law.

34:56.560 --> 34:58.110
Mr. Tang, don't drink alone.

34:58.110 --> 34:59.570
Let's all toast together.

34:59.590 --> 35:01.480
Okay, come on.

35:01.760 --> 35:03.620
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

35:07.510 --> 35:08.570
You must be hungry.

35:09.000 --> 35:09.760
Eat up.

35:10.070 --> 35:10.550
Okay.

35:10.670 --> 35:11.320
Hungry?

35:11.550 --> 35:12.070
Yes.

35:12.070 --> 35:13.730
There are barbecue pork buns.

35:14.070 --> 35:14.590
Look.

35:14.890 --> 35:16.190
The buns have blossomed.

35:16.190 --> 35:17.280
They look great.

35:28.030 --> 35:29.360
The old me

35:30.030 --> 35:31.160
was afraid to answer

35:31.480 --> 35:33.080
questions about happiness.

35:34.000 --> 35:35.840
Not because I was being difficult,

35:35.840 --> 35:37.900
nor because I wanted to spite anyone,

35:38.440 --> 35:39.360
but because...

35:39.910 --> 35:41.510
I didn't know how to describe

35:41.880 --> 35:43.610
things that don't belong to me.

35:45.880 --> 35:46.590
If you ask me

35:46.590 --> 35:47.990
to define happiness now,

35:48.360 --> 35:49.920
I might still draw a blank.

35:51.800 --> 35:54.000
Because happiness has no answer.

35:54.550 --> 35:56.410
Happiness is a tangible feeling.

35:57.070 --> 35:58.960
It's all these warm,

35:59.880 --> 36:00.810
bright moments,

36:01.320 --> 36:02.400
just like now.

36:43.630 --> 36:44.800
It's raining so hard.

36:44.800 --> 36:46.000
Will Zhenzhu make it?

36:46.400 --> 36:47.630
No one is answering at the shop.

36:47.630 --> 36:48.630
They must be closed.

36:48.630 --> 36:49.960
Let's wait a bit longer.

36:52.920 --> 36:58.330
[Happy Life Materials]

37:23.400 --> 37:25.260
Where are you going, Bai Zhenzhu?

37:28.760 --> 37:29.880
Have you eaten yet?

37:31.400 --> 37:31.880
Get her!

37:32.920 --> 37:33.380
Get her!

37:54.800 --> 37:57.280
She's not returning pages
or answering calls.

37:57.280 --> 37:59.010
I feel like something is wrong.

38:00.920 --> 38:01.550
Let's go check.

38:01.550 --> 38:02.000
Okay.

38:06.150 --> 38:07.010
Hello, Ge Jian.

38:08.480 --> 38:09.930
Something happened to Zhenzhu.

38:09.930 --> 38:10.730
Okay, I got it.

38:29.110 --> 38:29.640
Zhenzhu!

38:30.360 --> 38:31.020
How are you?

38:33.280 --> 38:34.000
What happened here?

38:34.000 --> 38:35.230
Zhenzhu, what happened?

38:35.230 --> 38:35.960
Who did this?

38:36.670 --> 38:37.960
It's okay. It's okay.

38:38.850 --> 38:40.070
Ge Jian, take her to the hospital.

38:40.070 --> 38:40.440
Okay.

38:40.730 --> 38:42.730
No need. It's just flesh wounds.

38:42.760 --> 38:44.160
I'm already bandaged up.

38:45.400 --> 38:47.030
It was Ke Yixiong's gang.

38:48.800 --> 38:49.730
How many of them?

38:50.760 --> 38:51.620
Seven or eight.

38:52.070 --> 38:53.330
Seven or eight people?

38:53.440 --> 38:54.400
Just flesh wounds?

38:54.400 --> 38:55.920
They ran away after the fight?

38:55.920 --> 38:56.450
Zhenzhu,

38:56.810 --> 38:57.630
no matter how skilled you are,

38:57.630 --> 38:58.860
you couldn't have beaten off

38:58.860 --> 38:59.530
7 or 8 men.

39:02.630 --> 39:03.280
Zhenzhu,

39:03.640 --> 39:04.550
at a time like this,

39:04.550 --> 39:05.550
tell us the truth.

39:08.320 --> 39:08.800
Well...

39:09.070 --> 39:10.510
San was here just now.

39:11.110 --> 39:12.550
He fought them off.

39:13.190 --> 39:14.190
Then where is San?

39:17.760 --> 39:18.760
Has San gone to chase

39:18.760 --> 39:19.560
those people?

39:20.150 --> 39:20.710
Zhenzhu,

39:21.110 --> 39:22.440
even if San is skilled,

39:22.710 --> 39:24.030
he's outnumbered.

39:25.320 --> 39:25.850
Zhenzhu,

39:26.400 --> 39:27.660
San is angry right now.

39:27.760 --> 39:28.880
If he hits too hard,

39:29.030 --> 39:30.830
he'll get himself into trouble.

39:31.960 --> 39:34.110
San didn't chase those thugs.

39:34.310 --> 39:35.240
He knew it must be

39:35.250 --> 39:36.530
Ke Yixiong's doing.

39:37.070 --> 39:39.070
He went straight to find Ke Yixiong.

39:39.400 --> 39:40.190
San said...

39:41.280 --> 39:42.940
however many injuries I have,

39:43.590 --> 39:45.070
he'll give the same to Ke Yixiong.

39:45.070 --> 39:46.530
He went to find Ke Yixiong?

39:48.760 --> 39:50.490
Xiaolan, I'm going to find San.

39:50.600 --> 39:51.480
I'll go with you.

39:51.480 --> 39:52.210
No need. You stay with them.

39:52.210 --> 39:52.920
Be careful!

39:53.030 --> 39:53.880
Stay safe!

40:02.000 --> 40:03.630
Ke Yixiong's stronghold in Longcheng

40:03.630 --> 40:05.520
has always been that mahjong parlor.

40:05.520 --> 40:06.210
When San gets there,

40:06.210 --> 40:08.010
he'll have to look for him there.

40:16.070 --> 40:16.530
Ms. Xia,

40:16.670 --> 40:17.200
Zhenzhu,

40:17.360 --> 40:18.840
you two talk. I'll keep watch outside.

40:18.840 --> 40:19.300
Thanks.

40:23.880 --> 40:24.410
Zhenzhu,

40:24.910 --> 40:26.230
come home with me tonight.

40:26.230 --> 40:28.560
I don't feel safe leaving you by yourself.

40:29.110 --> 40:30.800
Look at me, Xiaolan.

40:31.400 --> 40:32.510
I'll definitely behave myself

40:32.510 --> 40:34.070
and go home to sleep.

40:34.400 --> 40:36.150
If I go back with you and make noise,

40:36.150 --> 40:38.150
Granny Yu won't be able to rest well.

40:38.220 --> 40:40.030
Granny Yu doesn't mind a little noise.

40:40.030 --> 40:41.280
Stop making excuses.

40:46.280 --> 40:47.880
I didn't expect this either.

40:48.600 --> 40:50.080
Ke Yixiong is a sore loser.

40:50.110 --> 40:51.710
He acted like a cornered rat.

40:52.640 --> 40:53.710
San just wanted to help me

40:53.710 --> 40:54.760
get even.

40:56.590 --> 40:57.360
Zhenzhu.

40:58.030 --> 40:59.230
San's feelings for you

40:59.230 --> 41:00.630
are obvious to us all.

41:01.840 --> 41:03.300
But have you thought about

41:03.670 --> 41:06.110
what will happen
after San finds Ke Yixiong?

41:06.110 --> 41:07.000
Beat him up?

41:07.400 --> 41:09.030
Beat him until he's too scared
to mess with you?

41:09.030 --> 41:10.150
Do you think someone like Ke Yixiong

41:10.150 --> 41:11.350
will really let it go?

41:16.320 --> 41:16.850
Zhenzhu.

41:17.760 --> 41:19.560
Let's report this to the police.

41:21.000 --> 41:22.960
Report it because I got beaten?

41:23.280 --> 41:23.670
Yes.

41:24.230 --> 41:25.150
If you don't report it,

41:25.150 --> 41:27.480
how will the police know there's a victim?

41:27.480 --> 41:28.510
It was Ke Yixiong

41:28.510 --> 41:29.510
who broke the law.

41:29.840 --> 41:30.920
Let's report it now.

41:30.920 --> 41:32.650
Let's kick him while he's down.

41:33.880 --> 41:34.710
But today,

41:35.150 --> 41:37.150
it was just some thugs who hit me.

41:37.280 --> 41:39.320
Ke Yixiong didn't show up personally.

41:39.320 --> 41:40.520
They won't catch him.

41:41.080 --> 41:41.890
Those thugs

41:41.920 --> 41:43.320
had no grudge against you.

41:43.320 --> 41:44.650
The police will find out

41:44.840 --> 41:46.150
why they beat you.

41:46.840 --> 41:48.230
Even if we can't catch Ke Yixiong,

41:48.230 --> 41:49.320
catching a few of his men

41:49.320 --> 41:51.380
will still make things worse for him.

41:54.960 --> 41:55.710
Zhenzhu.

41:56.620 --> 41:58.590
Do you actually want
to run an honest business,

41:58.590 --> 42:01.390
or do you want
to follow in Ke Yixiong's footsteps?

42:02.970 --> 42:04.400
Did you lead the Bai Martial Arts School

42:04.400 --> 42:05.110
brothers

42:05.280 --> 42:06.680
to do something illegal?

42:08.190 --> 42:08.840
If you did,

42:09.190 --> 42:11.190
just pretend I never said anything.

42:28.550 --> 42:29.080
Yixiong.

42:29.360 --> 42:30.290
How is business?

42:30.360 --> 42:31.190
